  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then because I refused and he had also-- and when I was fit, I wanted to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I could-- and then I went to the Polish, this communication.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There was some kitchen help wanted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I went to the American kitchen together with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "In some picture I have, maybe here he is also there, Yurick in the picture.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We worked there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Very good because instead of money-- the money was little value.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We received PX rations exactly during the war like the American soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I remember there was only one-- one kind of soap, life soap.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Surely the young generation of Americans they do not know this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was not smelling nice, but against the [INAUDIBLE] very good for skin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then chocolate, very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Apples.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Fresh apples from California.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "In-- for German, it was money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Then I could deal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I could sell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I didn't smoke, so I sell the cigarette for some dress and shoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And then, when I had the experience with-- with some knowledge with English, because I bought, I received food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I grew up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I went to Dachau, to the officer's mess.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I was the assistant waiter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "My PX rations were still higher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I had many contacts, because among the American soldiers, even Polish immigrants were there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Once I met [? from ?] [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Torun. ?] He asked me also, don't go there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "There are Russians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Be careful.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Don't go there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But I say, then I go to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I will to-- I didn't tell him what the reason is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "But he said, Russia, in Vienna, in Austria there are also Russian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and when I was working there, Yurick had experience because he worked in Munich as a forced-- as a displaced person.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
